{"tid":1532834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家無謂再呃自己話我地嘅抗爭係正常","createTime":"2019-09-02T15:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T11:02:46.000Z","uid":233968,"like":120,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"85309e63e63ce844882a98487805af778f507e1d","tid":1532834,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:26:00.000Z","msg":"件事發展到依家，應該好多人都恨鐵不成鋼：老豆搵仔搵咗咁耐都未有popo出事、雞尾酒講咗成兩個幾月先正式有人玩、捉到藍絲廢老同落單popo都有左膠出嚟阻打人/冇人敢真係落手、和理非連閘都唔肯跳、工都唔肯罷等等。各種人地外國示威都習以為常嘅野，香港人就點都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日攞人數同畫面嚟打飛機，示威變示弱，屌極都唔醒，勇武衝到心淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢D叫示威？真係外國人笑popo都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗大家要承認一個事實，就係呢個係我地現時嘅極限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罷工罷到癱瘓香港，未做到；打到敵人殘廢，未做到；全民雞尾酒，未做到。我作為和理非的確覺得自己好廢，唔夠勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入正題，我未夠勇我認<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我覺得和理非可以做到嘅最大武器唔係love and peace，而係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">煩</span></span>。攬炒巴集會嗰日聽到陳浩天講呢點，我好認同，香港人真係好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />郁D就嗌痛嗌到全世界都聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連儂牆比人撕完再貼再撕再貼仲要貼得更大更靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每個星期有冇不反對通知書都照出嚟行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每晚十點鳩叫等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我地係咪已經將煩嘅極致表現無遺？我覺得未必<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日嘅情況我見到兩件事，第一，靠香港人罷工罷到做成大規模影響，真係冇乜可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第二，塞鐵成本已經變得極高，手足有送頭之危<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔係想話要停，但做呢兩件事嘅目的其實都係令社會運作成本增加，令政府管治失效，唔敢企出嚟做呢兩件事嘅和理非，應該都有方法暗中幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢排我自己做緊嘅野係 1.)專登係黨鐵爆人嗰陣夾硬塞入去(當然係上班族look)，用背囊飯盒偷偷地阻車門關上，等佢道門開合個兩三次；2.)係自己公司怠工：我係一間中資金融公司做客服，間公司做好多大陸人生意，呢排接到客戶嘅各種查詢啊開戶啊股票交收啊，一律扮睇唔到email<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />hea應跟緊啦跟緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />狂叫個客再提供資料話證監查得好嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />順手加多一兩句香港好亂暗示佢唔好嚟做生意等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總之極盡忽悠之能事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我先啱啱出嚟做咗幾個月野，對呢個社會嘅運作仲係一舊飯乜都唔太識<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，都唔知咁樣係咪真係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我暫時嘅成果係令公司走咗幾個客<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又冇咗幾個潛在客，中資公司喎令佢冇得賺梗係得心安理得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n我想話拋磚引玉出等大家討論下，作為唔敢出頭嘅和理非仲有d咩<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">煩</span></span>到社會嘅方法，大家一齊係自己崗位煩佢，應該比罷工更加影響社會運作，而政府同腦細又吹我地唔漲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f58ab7d29bb02dac99d3d6873ad617f777fb8d","tid":1532834,"uid":9049,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:28:17.000Z","msg":"8/9 14:00 美領事館<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>外爭港權，內除港賊</strong></span></span><br />\n（爭取民主人權法案，懲處賣港官員）<br />\n<br />\n「反送中」X「五四運動」<br />\n<br />\n#Chinazi<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JgCixJ0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJgCixJ0.png&h=8fa69f9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72133e5a571377503f7101ff4335292ea28e7295","tid":1532834,"uid":64153,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:28:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4027dade25f14102d12b4ff14887eeccaeda41ce","tid":1532834,"uid":266755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:29:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"28561b86d792ec8eb4c61666125d366224b2c254","tid":1532834,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed5fde400efdcac9449bb1b942a915f6363f235","tid":1532834,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:32:13.000Z","msg":"自推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a444a1fa725c0378f6d4fda9e10bbb35d825f9f9","tid":1532834,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f497d4fe182521ec169fa5d1f873144a32412416","tid":1532834,"uid":275785,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:36:41.000Z","msg":"其實罷工唔係請假.<br />\n唔理老細比唔比, 一於唔返工先叫罷工."},{"pid":"c028027a845d3d310cab9fc8c7390a3c05db158b","tid":1532834,"uid":311337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:37:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"952e28997d0d4b7972dcfda9728e921c71d4258d","tid":1532834,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:56:48.000Z","msg":"任何號召罷工嘅日子我都參加咗，612同85係請咗假，呢兩日交低咗句我罷工就冇直接冇返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw我諗我暫時未比人炒嘅原因係佢地未請到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f211e00c4ead696863ef00f1746e1d960d4a65","tid":1532834,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:57:12.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b3897ec0a17b6b4179f6273c393a0b03e1e881","tid":1532834,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c5f58ab7d29bb02dac99d3d6873ad617f777fb8d","tid":1532834,"uid":9049,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:28:17.000Z","msg":"8/9 14:00 美領事館<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>外爭港權，內除港賊</strong></span></span><br />\n（爭取民主人權法案，懲處賣港官員）<br />\n<br />\n「反送中」X「五四運動」<br />\n<br />\n#Chinazi<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JgCixJ0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJgCixJ0.png&h=8fa69f9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:59:40.000Z","msg":"過撚左一百年都唔撚明 <br />\n人地西方國家領教過血的教訓已經進步哂 中國呢? 原地踏步<br />\n一百年已經講緊民主自由 <br />\n而家仲想香港行呢套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f42cc7ec7e865a36c4cd92993195dc22bdaf3a8","tid":1532834,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:02:12.000Z","msg":"全城連儂牆<br />\n帶memo紙同幼marker出街 每10步貼一張"},{"pid":"9da44778fb3e4a3edd2d4cd8d57bba9e630d4732","tid":1532834,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T23:55:37.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"c26c0c3c7ce13215dadba4d35d48a1135a1105e7","tid":1532834,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T23:56:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81023d1096522dd986250711bd409a8853ef8a29","tid":1532834,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T23:56:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee390ca262769fc20e67875af34900019b6a3c1a","tid":1532834,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T23:56:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7c99fa52f40e5d0bbea114dc481890f9986bde0","tid":1532834,"uid":279326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:07:37.000Z","msg":"樓主做得好 大家keep住公民抗命"},{"pid":"808bf6c70db474f925216983ae9380041001c521","tid":1532834,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:14:09.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5854e0646c6c7f452588be0f8a1e1d289b57e1da","tid":1532834,"uid":64897,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:15:59.000Z","msg":"Pushhh"},{"pid":"dbef070ceb303b75d46309fe185ae7a4ce31dcc2","tid":1532834,"uid":59868,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d77bdcdabe4bcf2745b963f51e1c37ac2ca800e","tid":1532834,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:25:15.000Z","msg":"放映會計唔計煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfa3394cce6f49cb30504d99026e8b4b2acfa41","tid":1532834,"uid":263730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:33:50.000Z","msg":"其實半年前邊到係有人諗到係香港示威前線扔雞尾酒，仲要冇咩人割架，發夢好似仲聽到一大片歡呼聲。<br />\n進步緊架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbad7074b12c58c27867f88c397255061c028716","tid":1532834,"uid":263730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:35:45.000Z","msg":"之前超合作運動<br />\n1823係未停左？"},{"pid":"9227315b0c2e93b492e137d71d48be1ad217e26d","tid":1532834,"uid":242849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:43:24.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"d19e41336c4a3e253189db46cd51ba60d0122d02","tid":1532834,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dbef070ceb303b75d46309fe185ae7a4ce31dcc2","tid":1532834,"uid":59868,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:44:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891d6c7ad18af4609b2bd1d1a3ff6d4a4738bf1d","tid":1532834,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:44:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860d61504354d3df3e46e33229bccea7c1fb7f26","tid":1532834,"uid":233968,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d77bdcdabe4bcf2745b963f51e1c37ac2ca800e","tid":1532834,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:25:15.000Z","msg":"放映會計唔計煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:46:26.000Z","msg":"就我嗰區嚟講，十點鳩叫好似為藍絲帶嚟精神折磨，佢地應該覺得幾煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢地又唔敢學其他區咁屌返轉頭嫁喎，有D心涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d2e63f162267dbd4e43cd400e426e36324d5f9","tid":1532834,"uid":135248,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:53:41.000Z","msg":"香港人好善良架<br />\n我地示威者好有道德 <br />\n我地唔係無腦藍屍<br />\n唔好將自己變做魔鬼<br />\n唔好打呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8412158b3e9184b148e6acb99a60a637f6c9b61","tid":1532834,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:55:38.000Z","msg":"歐洲跳閘係一年365日<br />\n絕對無需要等抗爭<br />\n<br />\n香港都係學意大利擺軍人守逃票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccaf81a01328b2a8026dc1b8d22eb0ed1330400a","tid":1532834,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"891d6c7ad18af4609b2bd1d1a3ff6d4a4738bf1d","tid":1532834,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:44:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3433543d33a4bd8751d7ddf0dd562e273aa60b79","tid":1532834,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:57:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71324c7f35a64b26f9df5dcd2912dc47717a4b49","tid":1532834,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:58:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e0ec7c3238a13fbe208a6358301d1696524de04","tid":1532834,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46f814dbac6302b31c9f86b9ade2447dacead6a","tid":1532834,"uid":119524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:01:14.000Z","msg":"一句講西，be water<br />\ngear 唔夠人好，一定要快閃<br />\n<br />\n黨鐵咁多個站，popo來前，快拆快閃<br />\n<br />\nBe Water, 做真正快閃黨"},{"pid":"3a9d2345bd86464a057de9142c89006ca1b8e444","tid":1532834,"uid":313312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"85309e63e63ce844882a98487805af778f507e1d","tid":1532834,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:26:00.000Z","msg":"件事發展到依家，應該好多人都恨鐵不成鋼：老豆搵仔搵咗咁耐都未有popo出事、雞尾酒講咗成兩個幾月先正式有人玩、捉到藍絲廢老同落單popo都有左膠出嚟阻打人/冇人敢真係落手、和理非連閘都唔肯跳、工都唔肯罷等等。各種人地外國示威都習以為常嘅野，香港人就點都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日攞人數同畫面嚟打飛機，示威變示弱，屌極都唔醒，勇武衝到心淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢D叫示威？真係外國人笑popo都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗大家要承認一個事實，就係呢個係我地現時嘅極限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罷工罷到癱瘓香港，未做到；打到敵人殘廢，未做到；全民雞尾酒，未做到。我作為和理非的確覺得自己好廢，唔夠勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入正題，我未夠勇我認<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我覺得和理非可以做到嘅最大武器唔係love and peace，而係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">煩</span></span>。攬炒巴集會嗰日聽到陳浩天講呢點，我好認同，香港人真係好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />郁D就嗌痛嗌到全世界都聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連儂牆比人撕完再貼再撕再貼仲要貼得更大更靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每個星期有冇不反對通知書都照出嚟行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每晚十點鳩叫等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我地係咪已經將煩嘅極致表現無遺？我覺得未必<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日嘅情況我見到兩件事，第一，靠香港人罷工罷到做成大規模影響，真係冇乜可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第二，塞鐵成本已經變得極高，手足有送頭之危<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔係想話要停，但做呢兩件事嘅目的其實都係令社會運作成本增加，令政府管治失效，唔敢企出嚟做呢兩件事嘅和理非，應該都有方法暗中幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢排我自己做緊嘅野係 1.)專登係黨鐵爆人嗰陣夾硬塞入去(當然係上班族look)，用背囊飯盒偷偷地阻車門關上，等佢道門開合個兩三次；2.)係自己公司怠工：我係一間中資金融公司做客服，間公司做好多大陸人生意，呢排接到客戶嘅各種查詢啊開戶啊股票交收啊，一律扮睇唔到email<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />hea應跟緊啦跟緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />狂叫個客再提供資料話證監查得好嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />順手加多一兩句香港好亂暗示佢唔好嚟做生意等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總之極盡忽悠之能事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我先啱啱出嚟做咗幾個月野，對呢個社會嘅運作仲係一舊飯乜都唔太識<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，都唔知咁樣係咪真係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我暫時嘅成果係令公司走咗幾個客<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又冇咗幾個潛在客，中資公司喎令佢冇得賺梗係得心安理得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n我想話拋磚引玉出等大家討論下，作為唔敢出頭嘅和理非仲有d咩<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">煩</span></span>到社會嘅方法，大家一齊係自己崗位煩佢，應該比罷工更加影響社會運作，而政府同腦細又吹我地唔漲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:15:10.000Z","msg":"成日話中共紙老虎，又話無計。<br />\n其實真正無計係抗爭者，成個抗爭傷既傷，殘既殘，而我爭取到5大訴求邊樣，唔係失敗論，係事實論，傷人唔敢，想做又俾人阻止。<br />\n<br />\n由我話折祠堂果日都講，一次示弱，只會引到越來越多人打人斬人，而事實1.2個藍絲廢佬都夠收你成班抗爭者皮，<br />\n<br />\n黑警點解越來越過分，因為沒人阻止佢地，黑警先係做到不受傷不被捕<br />\n<br />\n依家保障大家第四權都俾人打，仲唔制止只會越來越過分同常態。"},{"pid":"bf18f7cbf2d376e47b6a73c9398917d16ba1fa08","tid":1532834,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:15:29.000Z","msg":"我想講我出呢個post嘅目原因係一嚟我唔太識打行動策略，二嚟除咗自己做緊嘅野我又真係比唔出具體建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但今次罷工真係搞唔起，記得617罷工嗰陣已經有人質疑我地罷工但又唔夠規模令全港癱瘓，淨係集會問心又冇乜用，咁我諗倒不如換個玩法，係自己崗位以影響甚至拖冧社會運作為目的地做個煩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果大家對自己係各行各業如何怠工有咩心得都歡迎提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8134fc2bdddde7c800bcca70908038fec3daa9","tid":1532834,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:31:05.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"dc0ab95e008f1d8218c903afe40fd66ed12ca7a1","tid":1532834,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436a20540e019f5b4081d7089fa15bfee585d8ba","tid":1532834,"uid":37135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:32:22.000Z","msg":"THX手足"},{"pid":"fb5df672f58ce161d6e6641a6680351b8c74e0c6","tid":1532834,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916b5c7ff098bf71df6c537ad2473c606de4abb9","tid":1532834,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:47:58.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"40b5d87169b6e6324e141b6cbc6833de5c806047","tid":1532834,"uid":207648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:05:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cd312dd7a56653aecf87b33cdbf67de50a72df29","tid":1532834,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:25:37.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"bd101e24f82152d6e81bf0c6bd8e0c6c144d299a","tid":1532834,"uid":281025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:37:40.000Z","msg":"大前晚發左個怪夢😪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11cc672f92e2d32643729b91c0012eee9c620e8","tid":1532834,"uid":233968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T